d 'XTMISPANEL': module to provide Comprehensive Missing Data Detection, Imputation and Diagnostics for Panel Data
d
d     xtmispanel is a comprehensive, all-in-one Stata command for
d handling missing values in panel    (time-series cross-sectional)
d data.   The command is designed specifically for panel data and
d respects the panel structure in all	 computations
d (panel-specific means, within-panel interpolation, panel-aware
d regression, etc.). 
d
d KW: panel data
d KW: missing data
d KW: diagnostics
d
d Requires: Stata version 15
d
d Distribution-Date: 20260304
d
d Author:   Merwan Roudane, NA
d Support: email  merwanroudane920@@gmail.com
d
f xtmispanel.ado
f xtmispanel.sthlp
f xtmispanel_test_all.do
f xtmispanel_impute.ado
f xtmispanel_graph.ado
f xtmispanel_example.do
